{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":577,"text":"Joe Kowan: I have stage fright."},{"time":2074,"text":"I've always had stage fright,"},{"time":3567,"text":"and not just a little bit,"},{"time":5395,"text":"it's a big bit."},{"time":7186,"text":"And it didn't even matter until I was 27."},{"time":9979,"text":"That's when I started writing songs, and even then"},{"time":12537,"text":"I only played them for myself."},{"time":14339,"text":"Just knowing my roommates were in the \nsame house made me uncomfortable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18084,"text":"But after a couple of years, \njust writing songs wasn't enough."},{"time":20891,"text":"I had all these stories and ideas,\nand I wanted to share them with people,"},{"time":23910,"text":"but physiologically, I couldn't do it."},{"time":27216,"text":"I had this irrational fear."},{"time":30142,"text":"But the more I wrote, and the more I practiced,"},{"time":32301,"text":"the more I wanted to perform."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33491,"text":"So on the week of my 30th birthday,"},{"time":35548,"text":"I decided I was going to go to this local open mic,"},{"time":38501,"text":"and put this fear behind me."},{"time":40216,"text":"Well, when I got there, it was packed."},{"time":43073,"text":"There were like 20 people there."},{"time":45047,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":46930,"text":"And they all looked angry."},{"time":49537,"text":"But I took a deep breath, and I signed up to play,"},{"time":53138,"text":"and I felt pretty good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54630,"text":"Pretty good, until about 10 minutes before my turn,"},{"time":57691,"text":"when my whole body rebelled, and \nthis wave of anxiety just washed over me."},{"time":63155,"text":"Now, when you experience fear, \nyour sympathetic nervous system kicks in."},{"time":66710,"text":"So you have a rush of adrenaline, \nyour heart rate increases,"},{"time":69553,"text":"your breathing gets faster."},{"time":71006,"text":"Next your non-essential systems start \nto shut down, like digestion. (Laughter)"},{"time":77178,"text":"So your mouth gets dry, and blood is routed\naway from your extremities,"},{"time":80542,"text":"so your fingers don't work anymore."},{"time":83142,"text":"Your pupils dilate, your muscles contract,\nyour Spidey sense tingles,"},{"time":86274,"text":"basically your whole body is trigger-happy.\n(Laughter)"},{"time":91448,"text":"That condition is not conducive \nto performing folk music."},{"time":96231,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":97800,"text":"I mean, your nervous system is an idiot."},{"time":100432,"text":"Really? Two hundred thousand years of human evolution, and it still can't tell the difference"},{"time":104242,"text":"between a saber tooth tiger and 20 folksingers"},{"time":106614,"text":"on a Tuesday night open mic?"},{"time":108685,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":110116,"text":"I have never been more terrified -- until now."},{"time":114173,"text":"(Laughter and cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":123248,"text":"So then it was my turn,"},{"time":125757,"text":"and somehow, I get myself onto \nthe stage, I start my song,"},{"time":128843,"text":"I open my mouth to sing the first line,"},{"time":131480,"text":"and this completely horrible vibrato --"},{"time":133443,"text":"you know, when your voice wavers -- \ncomes streaming out."},{"time":135930,"text":"And this is not the good kind of vibrato, \nlike an opera singer has,"},{"time":138543,"text":"this is my whole body just convulsing with fear."},{"time":141237,"text":"I mean, it's a nightmare."},{"time":142888,"text":"I'm embarrassed, the audience \nis clearly uncomfortable,"},{"time":145356,"text":"they're focused on my discomfort."},{"time":147709,"text":"It was so bad."},{"time":151484,"text":"But that was my first real experience \nas a solo singer-songwriter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155421,"text":"And something good did happen --\nI had the tiniest little glimpse"},{"time":158436,"text":"of that audience connection that I was hoping for."},{"time":160919,"text":"And I wanted more. But I knew \nI had to get past this nervousness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164927,"text":"That night I promised myself: \nI would go back every week"},{"time":168097,"text":"until I wasn't nervous anymore."},{"time":170032,"text":"And I did. I went back every single week,"},{"time":172915,"text":"and sure enough, week after week,"},{"time":176730,"text":"it didn't get any better. The same \nthing happened every week. (Laughter)"},{"time":180900,"text":"I couldn't shake it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182848,"text":"And that's when I had an epiphany."},{"time":184521,"text":"And I remember it really well, because I \ndon't have a lot of epiphanies. (Laughter)"},{"time":190532,"text":"All I had to do was write a song \nthat exploits my nervousness."},{"time":194161,"text":"That only seems authentic when I have stage fright,"},{"time":196283,"text":"and the more nervous I was,"},{"time":197571,"text":"the better the song would be. Easy."},{"time":200160,"text":"So I started writing a song about having stage fright."},{"time":204989,"text":"First, fessing up to the problem,"},{"time":207050,"text":"the physical manifestations, how I would feel,"},{"time":208878,"text":"how the listener might feel."},{"time":210307,"text":"And then accounting for things like my shaky voice,"},{"time":212915,"text":"and I knew I would be singing about a \nhalf-octave higher than normal,"},{"time":215847,"text":"because I was nervous."},{"time":217961,"text":"By having a song that explained \nwhat was happening to me,"},{"time":221033,"text":"while it was happening,"},{"time":222520,"text":"that gave the audience permission to think about it."},{"time":224383,"text":"They didn't have to feel bad \nfor me because I was nervous,"},{"time":227144,"text":"they could experience that with me,"},{"time":228862,"text":"and we were all one big happy, nervous, \nuncomfortable family. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":234111,"text":"By thinking about my audience, \nby embracing and exploiting my problem,"},{"time":238920,"text":"I was able to take something \nthat was blocking my progress,"},{"time":241855,"text":"and turn it into something that \nwas essential for my success."},{"time":245792,"text":"And having the stage fright song let \nme get past that biggest issue"},{"time":248812,"text":"right in the beginning of a performance."},{"time":250630,"text":"And then I could move on, \nand play the rest of my songs"},{"time":252174,"text":"with just a little bit more ease."},{"time":255428,"text":"And eventually, over time, I didn't \nhave to play the stage fright song at all."},{"time":261704,"text":"Except for when I was really \nnervous, like now. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":268945,"text":"Would it be okay if I played the \nstage fright song for you?"},{"time":271670,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":280753,"text":"Can I have a sip of water?"},{"time":283715,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":288143,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295442,"text":"♫ I'm not joking, you know, ♫"},{"time":298363,"text":"♫ this stage fright is real. ♫"},{"time":303991,"text":"♫ And if I'm up here trembling and singing, ♫"},{"time":307202,"text":"♫ well, you'll know how I feel. ♫"},{"time":311548,"text":"♫ And the mistake I'd be making, ♫"},{"time":315468,"text":"♫ the tremolo caused by my whole body shaking. ♫"},{"time":319396,"text":"♫ As you sit there feeling embarrassed for me, ♫"},{"time":322863,"text":"♫ well, you don't have to be. ♫"},{"time":325909,"text":"♫ Well, maybe just a little bit. ♫"},{"time":328424,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":329825,"text":"♫ And maybe I'll try to imagine \nyou all without clothes. ♫"},{"time":337704,"text":"♫ But singing in front of all naked strangers\nscares me more than anyone knows. ♫"},{"time":345577,"text":"♫ Not to discuss this at length, ♫"},{"time":349530,"text":"♫ but my body image was never my strength. ♫"},{"time":354775,"text":"♫ So frankly, I wish that you all would get dressed, ♫"},{"time":358313,"text":"♫ I mean, you're not even really naked. ♫"},{"time":363203,"text":"♫ And I'm the one with the problem. ♫"},{"time":366546,"text":"♫ And you tell me, don't worry \nso much, you'll be great. ♫"},{"time":373814,"text":"♫ But I'm the one living with me ♫"},{"time":376618,"text":"♫ and I know how I get. ♫"},{"time":378936,"text":"♫ Your advice is gentle but late. ♫"},{"time":383080,"text":"♫ If not just a bit patronizing. ♫"},{"time":386529,"text":"♫ And that sarcastic tone doesn't \nhelp me when I sing. ♫"},{"time":391361,"text":"♫ But we shouldn't talk about \nthese things right now, ♫"},{"time":395249,"text":"♫ really, I'm up on stage, and \nyou're in the crowd. Hi. ♫"},{"time":402136,"text":"♫ And I'm not making fun of \nunnurtured, irrational fear, ♫"},{"time":411359,"text":"♫ and if I wasn't ready to face this, ♫"},{"time":414275,"text":"♫ I sure as hell wouldn't be here. ♫"},{"time":418807,"text":"♫ But if I belt one note out clearly, ♫"},{"time":423945,"text":"♫ you'll know I'm recovering slowly but surely. ♫"},{"time":428231,"text":"♫ And maybe next week, I'll set my guitar ringin' ♫"},{"time":432194,"text":"♫ my voice clear as water, and everyone singin'. ♫"},{"time":436548,"text":"♫ But probably I'll just get up and start groovin', ♫"},{"time":440315,"text":"♫ my vocal cords movin', ♫"},{"time":443722,"text":"♫ at speeds slightly faster than sound. ♫"},{"time":456024,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}